<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" COLOR="#00AAFF">Originally posted by Sevok Celith'ar on 10-01-2000 08:18 PM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL"> [QUOTE]Originally posted by Gratpoche:
[b]I just wanted to know if my pet skeleton is an exp stealer and if so, I want to know how to maximize my exp profits.[/b][/QUOTE]

He is, to some degree.  If you are soloing, he will take some EXP whether he gets the killing blow or not.  If you are in a group, he only takes us EXP if he gets the killing blow.  So, in a group, use /pet back off at the last moment to make sure someone else gets the killing blow.

</TEXTAREA>
